{"id": 1043, "genre": 1001, "title": "你都做过哪些智能时代的小善举？", "description": "我，一个贯彻爱与正义的小仙女。（题目来自：Carson Ellis）", "record_count": 3676, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/201607021838379cB2px6kDXfyH7J5.jpeg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2016-06-14T11:00:03Z", "options": [{"id": 89088, "content": "看成…你都做过哪些智能时代的小公举…【微笑】", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 57300}, {"id": 89600, "content": "默默把那些从不发说说，只发广告的好友屏蔽掉", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 620309}, {"id": 88835, "content": "游戏里帮新人做任务", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 645107}, {"id": 97540, "content": "给各种苦逼的人捐款", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 466835}, {"id": 115462, "content": "看电影关弹幕", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 755861}, {"id": 88842, "content": "作为一个浙大同学很认真转发团委的微博", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 645107}, {"id": 90897, "content": "朋友圈点赞 投票", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 651629}, {"id": 88851, "content": "好棒啊", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 643965}, {"id": 88852, "content": "出国友情提供人肉代购", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 112264}, {"id": 88853, "content": "有个程序猿同事辞职以后就开始整天约妹子拍私房，然后发朋友圈。但是他的拍照技术一直很一般没什么长进。有一次终于发了露点图，没有露脸，然后我们直接点了举报，第二天他的朋友圈被微信删除了", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 193260}, {"id": 88855, "content": "用一款软件为远在千里之外的爸妈定了两张母亲节的电影票！", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 645137}, {"id": 88857, "content": "买智能手机 第一代入手 戴妃+，纸巾不能忘", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 635249}, {"id": 88858, "content": "给自己点赞", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 645163}, {"id": 88859, "content": "支付宝提现快", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 645175}, {"id": 88860, "content": "每天胖友圈点10个赞，跟他们说其实你很美", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 606751}, {"id": 88861, "content": "帮情侣团购电影票", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 632137}, {"id": 88862, "content": "给某宝用户提问回答", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 645185}, {"id": 88863, "content": "不乱转发是我最大的善意", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 630419}, {"id": 88864, "content": "这个模式虽然看起来比较漂亮，但可读性好差啊", "image": "img/option/option/20160702182638u3AGTwhjbX4QvcIo.jpg", "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 645179}, {"id": 88866, "content": "仔仔细细翻来覆去的看完别人发的黄图后，轻轻点了一下举报。?", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 634328}, {"id": 88867, "content": "地铁里遇到举着二维码求扫的创业者委婉拒绝，并向对方抛出一个问题：我也有公众号，关注一下吗？", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 186884}, {"id": 95524, "content": "只发美化的照片", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 668232}, {"id": 88869, "content": "举报咸鱼上的相机骗局..然而没什么卵用..", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 86697}, {"id": 88871, "content": "很少发朋友圈，环保环保", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 632190}, {"id": 88872, "content": "共享群邮教学弟“科学上网”", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 642890}, {"id": 88873, "content": "减少共享垃圾，还圈子一个清静", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 632190}, {"id": 88875, "content": "父母的朋友圈点赞", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 166753}, {"id": 88877, "content": "帮忙录的超市工作人员捡落在地上的商品", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 539396}, {"id": 88878, "content": "教妈妈在朋友圈发照，还是那种美美哒", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 539396}, {"id": 88879, "content": "从来不在B站弹幕剧透", "image": null, "praise_count": 41, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 642091}, {"id": 88880, "content": "好热闹", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 645273}, {"id": 88881, "content": "好奇心日报中给小编点赞", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 645273}, {"id": 90161, "content": "抄了好的句子，变成一封信", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 641292}, {"id": 88882, "content": "从来不拉票", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 500338}, {"id": 89906, "content": "不乱发自拍 保护大家眼睛", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 616857}, {"id": 88883, "content": "坚持不屏蔽微信朋友圈的广告商", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 644914}, {"id": 88884, "content": "朋友圈里秀恩爱", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 640856}, {"id": 88886, "content": "是朋友们的善举 我侄女得恶性肿瘤 都在帮转发", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 643101}, {"id": 88887, "content": "打酱油", "image": "img/option/option/201607021826139guV0523SftkhmwF.jpg", "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 645292}, {"id": 88888, "content": "从来不在朋友圈发广告", "image": null, "praise_count": 13, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 598641}, {"id": 88890, "content": "每次自拍照先磨皮美白瘦脸大眼之后再发朋友圈", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 642170}, {"id": 88891, "content": "在火车站和星巴克帮没带现金的人支付宝提现，也在奶茶店被路人帮助过。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 645308}, {"id": 88892, "content": "帮爸妈、爸妈的朋友、大龄亲友网购-_-#", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 508286}, {"id": 88893, "content": "帮助游戏新手", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 614974}, {"id": 88894, "content": "帮代购画头像", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 641194}, {"id": 88895, "content": "给爸妈买各种好东西", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 137066}, {"id": 88896, "content": "微信秒回", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 172176}, {"id": 88897, "content": "朋友圈评论每条都回", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 172176}, {"id": 89409, "content": "在晒娃的朋友圈下面留言\"好可爱丫\"", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 647396}, {"id": 88898, "content": "不算善举，就是学着父母教我的样子跟父母说智能手机的各种用法。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 626850}]}